==Tailoring==
Garlic can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring|Shirt And Belt]].  [[File:Shirt159.png|24px]]

==Quests==
Garlic is not used in any [[quests]].

